title: Macross Frontier OST 2- Nyan TRA
description:
This is the second soundtrack from the series, covering the second half...  Some great songs on it, especially Northern Frontier, Seikan Hokuo & the medley from the finale.  I put this one together after all the other OST 2 torrents died at 99.8% and I got my CD finally...  

320 kBit/44100 hz/ 16-bit

Megumi Nakajima
May'n ( May Nakabayashi )
Maaya Sakamoto

If you can buy your own copy, do so- supporting helps us get more Macross goodness!  (Of course, we people over here have to import- bloody Robotech corp. trademark stuff...)


I guess I'll have to update my "everything Macross frontier torrent" now, don't I?  :p



NOTE: The album is Nyan TRA, not Nyan Tora- I had already made the 'rent before I noticed that, but just thought you should know.
